CatDescriptText: Zoning notice reads in part: "...August 8, 1962...P. A. Blan has applied for a permit for the erection of a future 2 story 2 family dwelling at 252? [Webster?] Avenue...hearing Friday, May 17, [196?]..."
TitMainTitle: Man, possibly Earl "Heff" Martin, holding Pittsburgh Press newspaper with headline "U.S. Tightens Rein on Drugs, Tests" above zoning notice sign, in empty lot with boy in background
